來源如何造成負面的情緒狀態而導致犯罪或偏差。（20分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8d340db50acd", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114120", "c": "205", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "犯罪學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "監所管理員"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-57112235-moex-00052', 'judicial-57112235', 'judicial-57112235-moex-114-cc138910', 'sub-judicial-57112235-02', NULL, 'essay', '研究發現有一群慢性被害人（chronicalvictims），他們很容易在特定時間
